quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  21,30,"Avo vasingatendi havaoni here kuti denga nepasi zvakange zvakabatana kuva chinhu chimwechete, uye tikazvipatsanura? Uye takagadzira kubva kumvura chinhu chese chinorarama. Havangatendi zvino here"
  21,31,"Uye takava tinoisa panyika makomo akasimba kuti isave inozunguzika nawo, uye takagadzira mairi (nyika) nzira dzakafaranuka kuti vadarike, pamwe vangaratidzwa gwara rakatwasuka"
  21,32,"Uye takava (Allah) tinoita denga sehwikwiyo iro rakanyatsochengetedzwa. Asi vanoramba humboo hwaro (zuva, nyenyedzi, mwedzi, mhepo, makore, nezvimwe zvinhu)"
  21,33,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vakasika usiku nemasikati, uye zuva nemwedzi, chese chichifamba munzira yacho"
  21,34,"Uye hapana munhu (wenyama) watakaita kuti ararame nokusingaperi (haafi) iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) usati wavapo. Asi kana ukafa, vachagara zvachose here"
  21,35,"Chinhu chese (chinorarama) chicharavira rufu, uye tichava (Allah) tinokuedzai nezvakaipa pamwe nezvakanaka. Uye muchava munodzoswa kwatiri"
  21,36,"Uye avo vasingatendi (muIslaam) vakakuona (Muhammad (SAW)), vanokuita zvedambe (vanokunyomba) vachitaura vachiti: “Ndiye here uyu anotaura zvakaipa pamusoro panamwari venyu (zvidhori, midzimu)?” Havatendi mune yeuchidzo yemupi wengoni dzake (Allah)"
  21,37,"Munhu akava anosikwa aine hana nhete (asingazvibate). Ndichava (Allah) ndinokuratidzai maAayah angu (umboo, mutongo, marwadzo). Saka ndikumbirei kuti ndisava ndinomatumira nekuchimbidza"
  21,38,"Vanotaura (vasingatendi) kuti: “Vimbiso yacho ichauya rinhiko kana uchitaura chokwadi?”"
  21,39,"Dai avo vasingatendi vaiziva (mamiriro enguva) apo vachange vasingagoni kupumha (kudzima, kubvisa) moto kubva kuzviso zvavo, kana kubva kumashure kwavo, uye havambova vakabatsirwa"
  21,40,"Asi moto (wezuva rekutongwa) uchangouya kwavari vasingafungiri (vakavarairwa), uye uchavavhiringidza, uye havazowani simba rekuudzivirira, uye havambozorodzwi"
  21,41,"Zvirokwazvo, vatumwa vakauya usati wauya (Muhammad (SAW)) vakatukwa (nekusekwa), asi avo vaivatuka (vaiseka) vakakomberedzwa nazvo, izvo zvavaituka (nekuseka)"